content: Data migration in progress. Please wait.

comment.text: "This translation key is used to display a message indicating that data migration is in progress, prompting the user to wait. It appears in import processing steps within a data import process in the PortalSettings category."

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The French translation 'Migration des données est en cours d'exécution' is grammatically awkward. 'est en cours d'exécution' is overly formal and less natural.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Migration des données est en cours.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: While 'Veuillez patienter' is correct, it's quite formal. A more conversational and appropriate tone might be preferred.

The translation 'Migrare de date în desfășurare Vă rugăm așteptați' is not the most natural or idiomatic Romanian. A more natural phrasing would use 'în curs de desfășurare' instead of 'în desfășurare'. Also, 'Vă rugăm așteptați' is a bit formal for a technical interface.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Migrare de date în curs de desfășurare. Vă rugăm să așteptați.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The two sentences are concatenated without punctuation. A period or other appropriate punctuation mark would improve readability.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Migrare de date în curs de desfășurare. Vă rugăm să așteptați.
